org.activebpel.rt.bpel
Interface IAeProcessInfoEvent

All Superinterfaces:
IAeBaseProcessEvent, IAeEvent
All Known Implementing Classes:
AeProcessInfoEvent
public interface IAeProcessInfoEvent
extends IAeBaseProcessEvent

Interface for process information events. Events are reported to listeners via handleProcessInfoEvent().
